inputs.name: Query
inputs.value:
let endDateTime = now();
let startDateTime = ago(12h);
let trendBinSize = 30m;
let capacityCounterName = 'cpuLimitNanoCores';
let usageCounterName = 'cpuUsageNanoCores';
let containerWebApiSystemInternal = "engage-webapi-private";
Perf
| where InstanceName has containerWebApiSystemInternal
| where TimeGenerated < endDateTime
| where TimeGenerated >= startDateTime
| where ObjectName == 'K8SContainer'
| where CounterName == capacityCounterName
| summarize LimitValue = max(CounterValue) by InstanceName=extract('templafy(prod\\d{1})', 1, InstanceName), CounterName, bin(TimeGenerated, trendBinSize)
| project InstanceName, CapacityStartTime = TimeGenerated, CapacityEndTime = TimeGenerated + trendBinSize, LimitValue
| join (
    Perf
    | where InstanceName has containerWebApiSystemInternal
    | where TimeGenerated < endDateTime + trendBinSize
    | where TimeGenerated >= startDateTime - trendBinSize
    | where ObjectName == 'K8SContainer'
    | where CounterName == usageCounterName
    | project InstanceName=extract('templafy(prod\\d{1})', 1, InstanceName), UsageValue = CounterValue, TimeGenerated
    )
    on InstanceName
| project InstanceName, TimeGenerated, UsagePercent = UsageValue * 100.0 / LimitValue
| summarize UsagePercent = avg(UsagePercent) by bin(TimeGenerated, trendBinSize), InstanceName
| render timechart

inputs.name: Query
inputs.value:
// Slowest pages 
// What are the 3 slowest pages, and how slow are they? 
pageViews
| where notempty(duration) and client_Type == 'Browser'
| where name == 'Engage.WebApp' //and operation_Name has '/engage/documents/'
| extend total_duration=duration*itemCount, endpoint = replace('/engage/v/\\w+','/engage/v/***', replace('/engage/documents/\\d+','/engage/documents/***', operation_Name))
| summarize avg_duration=(sum(total_duration)/sum(itemCount)) by endpoint
| top 10 by avg_duration desc

content.Query:
browserTimings
| where isnotempty(totalDuration) and client_Type == 'Browser'
| where name == 'Engage.WebApp' //and operation_Name has '/engage/documents/'
| extend total_duration=totalDuration*itemCount, endpoint = replace('/engage','/', replace('/engage/','/', replace('/engage/v/\\w+','/engage/v/***', replace('/engage/documents/\\d+','/engage/documents/***', operation_Name))))
| summarize percentile_total_duration_5=percentiles(total_duration, 5, 50, 75) by endpoint
| sort by percentile_total_duration_75 + percentile_total_duration_50 + percentile_total_duration_5
| take (10)
| render barchart

inputs.name: Query
inputs.value:
// Response time trend 
// Chart request duration over the last 12 hours. 
// To create an alert for this query, click '+ New alert rule'
requests
| where timestamp > ago(1d) 
| where customDimensions.KubernetesNamespace == "engage"
| where success == True
| where url contains "/api/"
| summarize avg(duration) by name
| order by avg_duration desc 
| take 10 
| render barchart

content.Query:
requests
| where customDimensions["system_KubernetesNamespace"] == "engage" and success == True
| where url has "/api/" and name !has "GET Warmup/Warmup"
| summarize Duration=avg(duration) by Endpoint=name
| order by Duration desc 
| take 10 
| render barchart

inputs.name: Query
inputs.value:
customEvents
| where name == "EngageShareCreateDocument"
| summarize Shares=sum(itemCount) by user_AccountId
| order by Shares desc 
| take 10

content.Query:
customEvents
| where timestamp > ago(90d)
| where name == "EngageSharingFlowCompleted"
| where customDimensions["account_TenantState"] != "Test"
| extend TenantState = iif( isempty( customDimensions["account_TenantState"]), customDimensions["TenantState"], customDimensions["account_TenantState"] )
| extend Tenant = strcat(user_AccountId, " (", TenantState, ")")
| extend Shares =  customDimensions["event_NumberOfParticipants"]
| summarize Shares=sum(toint(Shares)) by Tenant
| order by Shares desc

content.Query:
browserTimings
| where isnotempty(totalDuration) and client_Type == 'Browser'
| where name == 'Engage.WebApp' //and operation_Name has '/engage/documents/'
| extend miscellaneousProccessingsDuration=(totalDuration - processingDuration - networkDuration )
| extend operation_Name = replace('^/engage$','/engage/', operation_Name)
| extend operation_Name = replace('/engage/v/\\w+','/engage/v/***', operation_Name)
| extend operation_Name = replace('/engage/documents/\\d+','/engage/documents/***', operation_Name)
| extend operation_Name = replace('/engage/reminder/\\d+/.+/','/engage/reminder/***/***/', operation_Name)
| extend operation_Name = replace('/engage/','/', operation_Name)
| summarize Average_Miscellaneous_Proccessings_Duration = avg(miscellaneousProccessingsDuration * itemCount), Average_Network_Duration = avg(networkDuration*itemCount), Average_DOM_Processing_Duration = avg(processingDuration*itemCount)  by operation_Name
| sort by Average_DOM_Processing_Duration + Average_Network_Duration + Average_Miscellaneous_Proccessings_Duration
| take (10)
| render barchart

inputs.name: Query
inputs.value:
pageViews 
| where name == "Engage.WebApp"
| where url has "templafy.com/engage/v/"
| project Resolution=tostring(customDimensions.ScreenResolution)//, EntryPoint=replace('(http)\\S+(templafy.com)', '', replace('/engage/v/\\w+','/engage/v/***', replace('/engage/documents/\\d+','/engage/documents/***', url))) 
| summarize CountByResolution=count() by Resolution
| order by CountByResolution
| render piechart

content.Query:
let events = dynamic(["EngageShareCreateDocument"]);
let queryTable = () {
    pageViews 
    | where name == "Engage.WebApp"
    | where url has "templafy.com/engage/v/"
    | project Resolution=tostring(customDimensions["client_ScreenResolution"])
    | summarize Events = count() by Resolution
};
let byCohortTable = queryTable
| project Events, dimension = tostring(Resolution)
| project Events, dimension = iif(dimension == "640*360","nHD",dimension)
| project Events, dimension = iif(dimension == "800*600","SVGA",dimension)
| project Events, dimension = iif(dimension == "1024*768","XGA",dimension)
| project Events, dimension = iif(dimension == "1280*720","WXGA",dimension)
| project Events, dimension = iif(dimension == "1280*800","WXGA",dimension)
| project Events, dimension = iif(dimension == "1280*1024","SXGA",dimension)
| project Events, dimension = iif(dimension == "1360*768","HD",dimension)
| project Events, dimension = iif(dimension == "1366*768","HD",dimension)
| project Events, dimension = iif(dimension == "1440*900","WXGA+",dimension)
| project Events, dimension = iif(dimension == "1600*900","HD+",dimension)
| project Events, dimension = iif(dimension == "1680*1050","WSXGA+",dimension)
| project Events, dimension = iif(dimension == "1920*1080","FHD",dimension)
| project Events, dimension = iif(dimension == "1920*1200","WUXGA",dimension)
| project Events, dimension = iif(dimension == "2048*1152","QWXGA",dimension)
| project Events, dimension = iif(dimension == "2048*1536","QXGA",dimension)
| project Events, dimension = iif(dimension == "2560*1080","UWFHD",dimension)
| project Events, dimension = iif(dimension == "2560*1440","QHD",dimension)
| project Events, dimension = iif(dimension == "2560*1600","WQXGA",dimension)
| project Events, dimension = iif(dimension == "3440*1440","UWQHD",dimension)
| project Events, dimension = iif(dimension == "3840*2160","4K UHD",dimension)
| project Events, dimension = iif(dimension has "*","others",dimension)
;
let topSegments = byCohortTable
    | top 5 by Events
    | summarize makelist(dimension);
let topEventMetrics = byCohortTable
    | where dimension in (topSegments);
let otherEventUsers = byCohortTable
    | where dimension !in (topSegments)
    | extend dimension = "others";
otherEventUsers
| union topEventMetrics
| summarize Events = sum(Events) by dimension
| order by dimension desc
| render piechart

inputs.name: Query
Query
inputs.value:
// Slowest pages 
// What are the 3 slowest pages, and how slow are they? 
pageViews
| where notempty(duration) and client_Type == 'Browser'
| where name == 'Engage.WebApp' //and operation_Name has '/engage/documents/'
| extend total_duration=duration*itemCount, endpoint = replace('/engage/v/\\w+','/engage/v/***', replace('/engage/documents/\\d+','/engage/documents/***', operation_Name))
| summarize avg_duration=(sum(total_duration)/sum(itemCount)) by endpoint
| top 10 by avg_duration desc

content.Query:

browserTimings

| extend endpoint = replace('/engage','/', replace('/engage/','/', replace('/engage/v/\\w+','/engage/v/***', replace('/engage/documents/\\d+','/engage/documents/***', operation_Name))))
| summarize view= count() by endpoint
| top 10 by view desc
| render barchart

inputs.name: Query

content.Query:
customEvents
    | where name == "EngageShareCreateDocument" and isempty(operation_SyntheticSource)
    | extend name = replace("\n", "", name), dimension = customDimensions["event_EntryPoint"]
    | extend dimension = iif(isempty(dimension), "<undefined>", dimension)
    | summarize events_Counts = count() by bin(timestamp, 1d), dimension

inputs.name: Query

content.Query:
exceptions
| where tostring(customDimensions["system_SystemName"]) == "engage"
| where type != "System.OperationCanceledException" and type != "System.Threading.Tasks.TaskCanceledException"
| join kind= leftouter (requests) on operation_Id
| project 
    exceptionType = type,
    operation_Id,
    timestamp,
    failedMethod = method,
    requestName = name
| summarize 
    ExampleOperationId=max(operation_Id),
    LastOcurrence=max(timestamp),
    count() by exceptionType,
    failedMethod,
    requestName
| order by
    ExampleOperationId,
    count_

inputs.name: Query
inputs.value:
requests
| where customDimensions["system_KubernetesNamespace"] == "preview-engine"
| where success == false
| join kind= inner (exceptions) on operation_Id
| project
    exceptionType = type,
    requestName = name,
    failedMethod = method,
    operation_Id,
    timestamp
| summarize ExampleOperationId=max(operation_Id), LastOcurrence=max(timestamp), count() by exceptionType, failedMethod, requestName
| order by count_
